Aku membunuh Hyung Dal Soo dua kali.

702
00:54:07,150 --> 00:54:09,490
Makanya aku tak boleh kalah denganmu.

703
00:54:10,410 --> 00:54:12,140
Mengerti?

704
00:54:25,360 --> 00:54:30,990
Asisten Choi. Maafkan aku.

705
00:54:30,990 --> 00:54:33,760
Kau baik-baik saja, Choi In Kyung?

706
00:54:36,180 --> 00:54:37,620
Ya.

707
00:54:37,620 --> 00:54:43,050
Syukurlah kalau kau baik-baik saja.

708
00:54:44,040 --> 00:54:45,780
In Kyung.

709
00:54:49,330 --> 00:54:50,330
Ya.

710
00:54:50,330 --> 00:54:52,800
Pergilah.

711
00:54:56,100 --> 00:55:05,770
Anggota Dewan.
Umumkan permintaan mereka.

